{"tid":2419031,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"英女皇出招  傳聯合查爾斯、威廉等皇室成員一起對戰梅根","createTime":"2021-02-23T04:58:35.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-23T10:14:36.000Z","uid":184679,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"90a667843e8b8384f3d846781c3caafc3932cb54","tid":2419031,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T04:58:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pgw.worldjournal.com/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/wj/realtime/2021/02/23/11751843.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=800&amp;exp=3600&amp;q=75&amp;nt=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.worldjournal.com%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2Fwj%2Frealtime%2F2021%2F02%2F23%2F11751843.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D800%26exp%3D3600%26q%3D75%26nt%3D1&h=ea0ffbb4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n伊莉莎白二世女王不願被孫子與孫媳耍著玩，也展開反擊的行動。（路透資料照片）<br />\n<br />\n英國王室的內訌，進來成為各方矚目焦點，執意要「最大分貝喊出內心聲音」的梅根，在英國不得人緣，被視為任性、耍賴，她將在歐普拉的電視訪問中首度對外公開談到家人之間的衝突， 各方好奇究竟會有何勁爆內容，王室更擔心再被她破壞形象，決定先發制人，在她的歐普拉訪問播出前一天， 搶先安排伊莉莎白二世女王在「大英國協日電視演說」亮相，屆時她也可能會傳達王室的立場，不讓梅根專美，查爾斯王子、威廉王子等其他王室重要成員都會在節目中出現，齊心協力面對梅根帶來的新風暴。<br />\n<br />\n傳統、保守的英國王室被從美國來、不習慣委屈自己的梅根攪得天翻地覆，從她的丈夫哈利王子宣告要卸下王室重要成員身分，到兩人搬至美國居住，再到跟一堆媒體大品牌合作賺進豐厚利潤等，一直在挑戰王室的容忍極限。女王決定剝奪兩人在英國僅存的一些單位「王家贊助人」身分後，他們發布了語意帶反擊的聲明，被視為對女王大不敬，戰火再度點燃，這次將如何收場？外界密切注意。<br />\n<br />\n據傳歐普拉早在女王宣告哈利、梅根脫離王室公務成員身分之前就已錄好訪談，那時哈利和梅根還都以為自己仍在英國沒有完全斷絕任何關係、還保有少數單位的皇家贊助人身分，現在與王室幾乎等於徹底切割，部分訪問內容也完全不符合最新情況，不是得修剪掉，就是得重錄，女王仍然有辦法令梅根無法稱心如意，並非省油的燈。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pgw.worldjournal.com/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/wj/realtime/2021/02/23/11751842.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=800&amp;exp=3600&amp;q=75&amp;nt=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.worldjournal.com%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2Fwj%2Frealtime%2F2021%2F02%2F23%2F11751842.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D800%26exp%3D3600%26q%3D75%26nt%3D1&h=f2a529d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n梅根和哈利在美國一再試探英國王室的底線，屢屢造成彼此的衝突。（路透資料照片）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.worldjournal.com/wj/story/121617/5270086\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.worldjournal.com%2Fwj%2Fstory%2F121617%2F5270086&d=w4lkeVluhl8nqpRa%2FCUv32lERb1kSGFVDbesiz0gOXg%3D&h=6f19d9ce\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.worldjournal.com/wj/story/121617/5270086</a>"},{"pid":"5b0208ef00503af94582c041b9f6b390c4762c5f","tid":2419031,"uid":219470,"like":15,"dislike":5,"score":10,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T05:00:36.000Z","msg":"好悶呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> plan多次車禍咪得 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"451a4ccb8d7e58115aa593ae9304629676c8008e","tid":2419031,"uid":370061,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"quote":{"pid":"5b0208ef00503af94582c041b9f6b390c4762c5f","tid":2419031,"uid":219470,"like":15,"dislike":5,"score":10,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T05:00:36.000Z","msg":"好悶呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> plan多次車禍咪得 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T05:04:30.000Z","msg":"脫離皇室，憑咩嘢用皇室嘅名呃飯食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"071a4f21bae9e5878b69d7f95c2a34efab712aca","tid":2419031,"uid":95357,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"quote":{"pid":"5b0208ef00503af94582c041b9f6b390c4762c5f","tid":2419031,"uid":219470,"like":15,"dislike":5,"score":10,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T05:00:36.000Z","msg":"好悶呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> plan多次車禍咪得 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T05:23:21.000Z","msg":"我相信今次plan應該冇乜英國人會不滿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ed9fc5ba5163987f7e1f9c4e44b46d19cf97842","tid":